gujarati.context:
I known the wing flew away in a hurry, got tired; 
A friend remained with me at home, I saw; 
Did not reach anyone together in unity.

I will come with you if you are not willing; 
We won't reach with us then together; 
Saying this, we tied the thread of love, 
And after that we walked hand in hand.

Here is the translation:

There went Lalala, the colored one, from there; came Valvami ji Vartal;

I became acquainted with his friends; came with my family to see everyone.

This is the translation:

This beginning and many virtues, filled their neighbor's dish; 
Those seated there are alive, those who came there are Harijan.

Ati apara aksharati, thai tame te saathe prit;
Bhakt jakt maahi chhe jo ghana, upasak avatara tana.

Extremely infinite letters are at, that is with you; 
Devotee of great soul is in me who many, worshipper of the avatar yours.
